              "name": "One Action",
              "subtype": "action_type",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "effect": "Using their prior attack to shift their opponent's guard, the spinecracker makes a melee Strike with one hand. If it hits, they grab the target using their other hand. The creature remains grabbed until the end of the spinecracker's next turn or until it Escapes, whichever comes first.",
